ownerOnlyFolders: Array of folder names which contain owner-only commands. Case insensitive. Defaults to owner-only
HideOverwriteWarning: true/false. Hides the "Overwriting following variables and functions" warning, Defaults to false
HideNonBetaCommandLog: true/false. Hides the info that a non-beta slash command has been skipped. Defaults to false
HideDisabledCommandLog: true/false. Hides the info that a disabled command has been loaded to client.prefixCommands/client.slashCommands. Defaults to false
replyOnDisabledCommand: true/false. Reply with an error message if a disabled command is run. Defaults to true
replyOnNonBetaCommand: true/false. Reply with an error message if a non-beta command is run. Defaults to true
